name: Archives - 01 - Anonymous dancer in Hackney, London, on 04/05/2005
description: Photo taken on May 4th 2005 in Shoreditch, London, most likely during a Secretsundaze party at the mythological “The Poet”. One physical copy of this, printed on Dibond, exists somewhere in Italy. Shot with a Sony DSC-T1 pocket-sized camera by Matteo Manzini @matteomanzini__ (Twitter/Instagram). “Still based in Milan but travelling back and forth, I was doing a lot of people watching around East London at that time, trying to take visual notes of the highlights.”.
